{"tid":2513499,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"哥倫比亞 爆發反稅務改革示威, 已經有14人死亡","createTime":"2021-05-02T14:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:28:16.000Z","uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f19a4deb5aa107c544ba6119b2193ffd9d8be76","tid":2513499,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/intnews/20210502/photo/bkn-20210502130037362-0502_00992_001_01b.jpg?20210502204811\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fintnews%2F20210502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210502130037362-0502_00992_001_01b.jpg%3F20210502204811&h=c06e5963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哥倫比亞上周三（4月28日）起爆發反稅務改革示威，示威上周六（5月1日）踏入第4日，首都波哥大、第三大城市卡利等多地爆發衝突。有人權組織指，連日示威已造成14人死亡，179名平民及216名警員受傷。<br />\n民眾不滿稅務改革包括對公共服務及部分食物徵收消費稅，多地連日有人上街抗議，總統杜克上周五（4月29日）讓步宣布擱置開徵消費稅，但未能平息民憤。<br />\n多個城市上周六有民眾堵路、與警方衝突，波哥大出動防暴警察驅散示威者，卡利則有人搶掠及燒巴士。人權組織指控，卡利有警方濫權的情況。杜克同日表示，會派軍方到暴力風險高的城市協助控制場面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EoVXcDMSUcs&amp;ab_channel=AlexKrivosheya\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEoVXcDMSUcs%26ab_channel%3DAlexKrivosheya&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=df56c50b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EoVXcDMSUcs&amp;ab_channel=AlexKrivosheya</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEj44v6T_vs&amp;ab_channel=Ruptly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqEj44v6T_vs%26ab_channel%3DRuptly&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtYmB5A%2F6U2CfHiGB6dLXW7A%3D&h=7f46a8d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qEj44v6T_vs&amp;ab_channel=Ruptly</a><br />\n<br />\n發現大部份示威者同防暴警 都唔戴口罩"},{"pid":"dbe14e0cb3f20e9b306f08740fda51e665bc7852","tid":2513499,"uid":41575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"網上有示威者爆頭相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" clas